data.description: NEW IMPROVEMENTS TO THIS MOVE IN READY HOME! Complete AC Duct Work Replacement just completed making the New AC unit extremely efficient. This lovely upgraded 4-bedroom, 2 bath home with den and fenced yard is located in the gated community of Varsity Lakes is here for you and your family! Varsity lakes, with its charming play area and low HOA fees, is also within walking distance of schools. Close to Restaurants, shopping, entertainment and the airport.  The house has been exquisitely decorated with stunning modern light fixtures, ceiling fans, and sinks. The bedrooms are split on both sides of the house offering privacy and peace and quiet. There is the perfect den/flex space for a home office.  New Backsplash, New Stove, New Microwave, New Dishwasher and the Perfect Coffee Bar! It doesn't stop there... Newly tiled master bathroom with dual sinks, dual shower with Bluetooth speaker!  ALSO... NEW AIR CONDITIONER & HANDLER installed in 2022!  ROOF 2018!  You will never have to worry about an outrageous electric bill!  NEW SOLAR PANELS (Dec 2022)!  The screened in lanai sporting a doggie door and fenced yard overlook a canal!  No Hurricane Damage!  NO FLOOD ZONE!  MOTIVATED SELLERS!
